{"tid":2305420,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"Jk IELTS 補習","createTime":"2020-11-29T15:19:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-24T04:51:16.000Z","uid":377497,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"78e11fd87693093833562a28746cf3cf74d49710","tid":2305420,"uid":377497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T15:19:24.000Z","msg":"想問有冇人補過JK IELTS ? 好唔好？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我自己英文得2 ，想考6.0 / 6.5 <br />\n<br />\n想問各位師兄姐有乜意見，或者點樣備考。<br />\n<br />\nIELTS 係咪自修已經夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3ee6e6549bcbec54e482e5e44695f7c70c89af6","tid":2305420,"uid":305866,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T15:35:12.000Z","msg":"英文得2就聽Ted talk 、睇SCMP打返好底先。身邊英文唔好嘅朋友補完習最後都係考得唔好，補習冇太大作用。"},{"pid":"ec2a5fca3f42bec48f7d4bf9f9d19175cfff764f","tid":2305420,"uid":210944,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T17:09:23.000Z","msg":"past paper = enough"},{"pid":"453810bcb4bc1b2c4af1e9db1fe6302fe34a3c4b","tid":2305420,"uid":126510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T14:59:41.000Z","msg":"lv2個range好大<br />\n勁既可以6.5<br />\n廢既得4.5 <br />\n當然大部分人都係5-5.5 <br />\n你dse細分幾多？<br />\n可以做兩套pp睇下自己點先"},{"pid":"a36be559c366d18ea3c95a72eae7b7fdd57fd6ff","tid":2305420,"uid":304957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T15:45:53.000Z","msg":"本來都諗住報，但係最後都冇<br />\n個人覺得價錢唔貴，有冇用就因人而異啦<br />\n我靠操pp，最後7咗 （dse3）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fb310b6bf74dea1703017bdef73fbf40c449aec","tid":2305420,"uid":25055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a36be559c366d18ea3c95a72eae7b7fdd57fd6ff","tid":2305420,"uid":304957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T15:45:53.000Z","msg":"本來都諗住報，但係最後都冇<br />\n個人覺得價錢唔貴，有冇用就因人而異啦<br />\n我靠操pp，最後7咗 （dse3）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" cl